@startuml
title Gestione della Memoria Conversazionale

actor       Studente       as S
participant "Frontend"       as FE
participant "Main.py" as API
participant "OrchestratorAgent"         as ORC
participant "ClassifierAgent"           as CLA
participant "GeneratorAgent"            as GEN
participant "RevisionAgent"             as REV
database    "localStorage\n(browser)"  as LS

' ─── Turno N - invio messaggio ───────────────────────────────
S -> FE : digita e invia messaggio

FE -> FE : aggiunge userMessage\na conversation[]

FE -> FE : costruisce conversationHistory\n.filter(user | agent)\n.slice(-10)\n.map(role, content)\n──────────────────────\nmax 10 msg = 5 scambi

FE -> LS : salva conversation[] aggiornata

FE -> API : POST { query,\n  user_info,\n  conversation_history[10] }

' ─── Orchestrator → AgentState ───────────────────────────────
API -> ORC : process_query(\n  query,\n  user_info,\n  conversation_history[10]\n)

ORC -> ORC : inizializza AgentState\n{ query, conversation_history[10],\n  user_status, user_name,\n  user_course, user_year, ... }

' ─── Step 1: Classifier ──────────────────────────────────────
ORC -> CLA : classify(\n  query,\n  user_context,\n  conversation_history[10]\n)

CLA -> CLA : prende gli ultimi 4 msg\nconversation_history[-4:]\n(= 2 scambi recenti)\nli inserisce come testo\nprima della domanda

CLA --> ORC : { category, description,\n  confidence }

ORC -> ORC : state[category] = ...

' ─── Step 2: Generator ───────────────────────────────────────
ORC -> GEN : generate(\n  query, category,\n  user_context,\n  conversation_history[10]\n)

GEN -> GEN : costruisce messages[]:\n  [SystemMessage(prompt)]\n  + TUTTI i 10 msg come\n    HumanMessage / AIMessage\n  + HumanMessage(query corrente)

GEN --> ORC : { response, category_used }

ORC -> ORC : state[generated_response] = ...

' ─── Step 3: Revisor ─────────────────────────────────────────
ORC -> REV : revise(\n  original_query,\n  generated_response,\n  category, user_context,\n  conversation_history[10]\n)

REV -> REV : prende gli ultimi 4 msg\nconversation_history[-4:]\nli inserisce come testo\nnel prompt di revisione

REV --> ORC : { revised_response,\n  has_changes }

ORC -> ORC : state[final_response] = ...

' ─── Risposta al frontend ─────────────────────────────────────
ORC --> API : { response, agent_used,\n  metadata }

API --> FE : { response, metadata }

FE -> FE : aggiunge agentMessage\na conversation[]

FE -> LS : salva conversation[] aggiornata

FE --> S : mostra risposta


@enduml